{
  "stem": "2133.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They used to bomb it all the time, the Americans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and we went and cleaned up after the bomb.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it was about four miles from the-- from the gasoline refinery.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had to go with the feet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had those wooden shoes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we weren't allowed to wear the shoes until we were going to the-- to the place, the working place.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had to put our shoes on our-- our shoulder.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had to go with bare feet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That you shouldn't wear it out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You shouldn't wear it out until we-- you know, except just for the work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So some of the fathers-- there were young fathers, were about-- I would say-- under 50, 45.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they had grown sons, like I, myself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we all marched every day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And some of those fathers, they couldn't walk as well as the youngsters.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they were beaten every single day until we got there-- four miles, four or five miles, something like that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And some of the fathers, I seen that their feet got infected.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
